    <item>
      <title>标准普尔称印度企业集团将在 10 年内投入 8000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indian-conglomerates-to-spend-800-billion-in-10-years-s-p-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，印度企业集团在追求增长的同时，也让经济走上更加绿色的未来道路，未来 10 年，印度企业集团的资本支出将比前 10 年增加近三倍，达到 8000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indian-conglomerates-to-spend-800-billion-in-10-years-s-p-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求疲软导致中国贷款表现令人失望，但债券提振信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管信贷增长超过预期（主要得益于国债销售激增），9月份中国贷款扩张表现令人失望，表明国内需求仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其公司赢得中国拒绝的 27 亿欧元乌干达铁路交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/turkish-firm-wins-bid-to-build-uganda-railway-that-china-shunned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yapi Merkezi Holdings AS 签署了一项价值 27 亿欧元（29.5 亿美元）的协议，在乌干达修建一条铁路，重启了这个在中国撤回支持后难以找到融资的项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/turkish-firm-wins-bid-to-build-uganda-railway-that-china-shunned</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 08:33:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购公司 MBK 收购金属巨头股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/deadline-looms-in-bitter-feud-for-control-of-korea-metals-empire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[收购公司 MBK Partners 表示，其已成功获得韩国锌业公司 5.34% 的股份，这一对全球最大锌冶炼厂控制权的争夺战标志着数十亿美元继承权之争的结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/deadline-looms-in-bitter-feud-for-control-of-korea-metals-empire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 23:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
